{"tid":339363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[你大我呀]馬時亨：高鐵總站每月營運費用八千萬","createTime":"2017-07-29T04:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T12:55:54.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24ceba895b81ee5de8a2c1ad45c181a9bb342712","tid":339363,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:06:28.000Z","msg":"營運費用八千萬一個月，當你上廣州收300，即係每日要26萬人來往廣州先收得返喎，即係，一抽膠鐵坐滿係一千人，你一日要來回開到260班先得，一日18個鐘營運，即係一個鐘要對開7班，每9分鐘開一班，咁你咪仲勁過廣深舊段d動車?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=230182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D230182&d=zD9qubVoP8tvnCVHFqtzmROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3704222d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D230182&h=33501504\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=230182</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府預計廣深港高鐵明年第三季通車，港鐵主席馬時亨接受本台專訪指出，若屆時立法會未能通過一地兩檢方案，高鐵便無法通車，情況是「蘇州過後無車搭」，屆時每月八千萬元營運費等同「倒落海」，呼籲社會理性討論方案。<br />\n<br />\n政府公布高鐵一地兩檢方案，西九總站約四分之一地方將劃為「內地口岸區」實施內地法律，引起民主派議員反對。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨接受本台專訪時表示，如果方案未能趕及在明年立法會休會前通過，明年第三季將不能通車。馬時亨預計今年年底前，可與政府達成高鐵的營運協議，預計高鐵項目的人手編制約有700人，並會加強培訓。<br />\n<br />\n至於高鐵通車後確實的班次、來往的地點、票價以至港鐵附例如何應用在營運高鐵之中，馬時亨說仍有待特區政府與內地當局商討後公布詳情。"},{"pid":"63bf75206bc9637b0c728fcf4096d332b8db114d","tid":339363,"uid":37661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母！<br />\n<br />\n五十年回本，回你老母呀！<br />\n<br />\n支那建國果陣同班豬講50年後你哋就開始搵到錢，睇下班豬會唔會仲支持你個仆街政權丫！"},{"pid":"8d9428b6fbe8e30123d314d4b487f17259e83425","tid":339363,"uid":69098,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"不如講下點樣每個月8000萬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23693dbb9bd5596a0a5a0b130a102e1d464cc587","tid":339363,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如講下點樣每個月8000萬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚大個站，冷氣費，燈光費都唔細數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b76e4caaa336ade296649de6c2ce385642655e0","tid":339363,"uid":100016,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"高層人工共六千萬"},{"pid":"5efa1bc94ebe290cb76480d3be8fe664e49a50f2","tid":339363,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:22:41.000Z","msg":"維穩費，且要美金，人弊唔穩陣"},{"pid":"55c27b8dd4b6dbc9e51d29d5201e83590f06c8a7","tid":339363,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"不如港鐵自己炸左佢啦"},{"pid":"60233166997befb80c929052585bf3447765cc69","tid":339363,"uid":91633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"即係同你講開通後要預左蝕好撚多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e928dba4cff374aa4113968bf3884a7d3cdd89","tid":339363,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係同你講開通後要預左蝕好撚多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔營運, 就乜問題都解決晒！"},{"pid":"330b4aa869b831178d56e114e0856ec1327d866b","tid":339363,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"有冇其他站比較下"},{"pid":"ecaa6517ecd5681292b9a4b1c859833d98784a51","tid":339363,"uid":49853,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"每月營運費都八千萬,仲未計建造費900億<br />\n想回本真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd05d73251372ba57cdf5124d04004d63a18b120","tid":339363,"uid":15815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"100 年都唔會回本"},{"pid":"5eaa05e60a3044e0145921a0791d0b9e184408e9","tid":339363,"uid":79563,"like":18,"disl